#Repost @unboundfortworth
・・・
WEAR BLUE this Thursday and join us by observing the United Nation’s World Day Against Trafficking in Persons, July 30. Snap a selfie of yourself in blue with the tag @unboundfortworth. 

Join the fight on a local level by becoming a monthly supporter of Unbound or helping provide donations for survivors. Find out more out at unboundfortworth.org.

#notinmycity #endtrafficking #ignitehope #worlddayagainsttrafficking #worlddayagainsttraffickinginpersons #worlddayagainsthumantrafficking #fortworth #texas #humantrafficking #sextrafficking
